__SqlaTable__.sql:
select distinct 
name as "Gender"
from public.hm_ret_gender_dim

select 
'Year of Entry' as "DynamicDimension"
UNION 
select 
'Year of Study'
UNION 
select 
'Gender'
UNION 
select 
'Federal Cohort'
UNION 
select 
'Ethnicity'
UNION 
select 
'Enrollment Status'
UNION 
select 
'Age Group'
UNION 
select 
'ACT score'
UNION 
select 
'Took Remedial course(s)'
UNION 
select 
'High School GPA'
UNION 
select 
'Pell Recipient (1st year)'

select 
t6.degreegroup as "Program"
from public.hm_ret_degreegroup_dim t6
order by 1

select 
{{ "\"" + " ', '".join(filter_values('DynamicDimension')) + "\""}} as "Dimension",
--x."Gender" as "Dimension",
x."Year of Entry",
x."Year of Study",
x."Gender",
x."Federal Cohort",
x."Ethnicity",
x."Enrollment Status",
x."Age Group",
x."GPA credits, pre-Entry",
x."Residency Status",
x."Took Remedial course(s)",
x."ACT score",
x."Pell Recipient (1st year)",
x."High School GPA",
x."Courses",
x."Program",
x.course_key,
x.gradepoints,
x.minutesabsent,
x.minutesattended,
x.dfw_flag,
x.crs_drop_flag,
x.timespent
from 

(select 

t4.year as "Year of Entry",
cast(t44.year as text) as "Year of Study",
t8.name as "Gender",
concat(t6.degreegroup,'-',t10.name) as "Federal Cohort", -- Revisit , t10.code = F,H,L,Q
t11.name as "Ethnicity",
t10.name as  "Enrollment Status",
case 
               when t1.age < 17 then '<17' 
               when t1.age >= 18 and t1.age <= 23 then '18-23' 
               when t1.age >= 24 and t1.age <= 29 then '24-29' 
               when t1.age >= 30 and t1.age <= 35 then '30-35' 
               when t1.age >= 36 and t1.age <= 40 then '36-40'
               when t1.age >= 41 and t1.age <= 45 then '41-45'
               when t1.age >= 46 and t1.age <= 50 then '46-50'
               else '>50' end as "Age Group",

t1.studenttermpreentrygpacredits as "GPA credits, pre-Entry",
t1.residency_status as  "Residency Status",

case 
when t1.remedialflag = 1 then 'Remedial' 
when t1.remedialflag = 0 then 'No Remedial' else 'Undefined' end as "Took Remedial course(s)",

case 
                              when t1.act_score <= 20 then 'ACT 20 or less' 
                              when t1.act_score >= 21 and t1.act_score <= 25 then 'ACT 21-25' 
                              when t1.act_score >= 26 and t1.act_score <= 30 then 'ACT 26-29' 
                              when t1.age >= 30 then 'ACT 30 or more'
                              else 'No ACT' end  as "ACT score",

case when t1.pellrecepient = 'N' then 'No' when t1.pellrecepient = 'Y' then 'Yes' else 'Undefined'
end as "Pell Recipient (1st year)",

case 
when t1.hsgpa >= 0.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 1.99 then '0.00-1.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 2.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 2.49 then '2.00-2.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 2.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 2.99 then '2.50-2.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 3.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 3.49 then '3.00-3.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 3.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 3.99 then '3.50-3.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 4.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 4.49 then '4.00-4.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 4.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 4.99 then '4.50-4.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 5.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 5.49 then '5.00-5.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 5.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 5.99 then '5.50-5.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 6.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 6.49 then '6.00-6.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 6.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 6.99 then '6.50-6.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 7.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 7.49 then '7.00-7.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 7.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 7.99 then '7.50-7.99'
else '>=8.00' end as "High School GPA",

t13.name as "Courses",
t6.degreegroup as "Program",

t1.course_key,
t1.gradepoints,
t1.minutesabsent,
t1.minutesattended,
t1.dfw_flag,
t1.crs_drop_flag,
t1.timespent



from ret_stdnt_crs_fact t1
left outer join public.hm_ret_year_dim t4 on t1.year_of_entry_key =t4.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_year_dim t44 on t1.year_of_study_key =t44.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_degreegroup_dim t6 on t1.degreegroup_key = t6.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_gender_dim t8 on t1.gender_key = t8.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_enrlstat_dim t10 on t1.enrollstatus_key = t10.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_ethnicities_dim t11 on t1.ethnicities_key  = t11.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_course_dim t13 on t1.course_key = t13.skey) x

select 
name as  "Enrollment Status"
from 
public.hm_ret_enrlstat_dim

select distinct 
year as "Year of Entry",
cast(year as text) as "Year of Study"
from public.hm_ret_year_dim
where year >= 2017 and   year <= 2022

select
DISTINCT 

case 
when t1.remedialflag = 1 then 'Remedial' 
when t1.remedialflag = 0 then 'No Remedial' else 'Undefined' end as "Took Remedial course(s)"

from ret_stdnt_fact t1
order by 1

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.
select distinct name as "Ethnicity" from public.hm_ret_ethnicities_dim

select
DISTINCT 

case 
		when t1.age < 17 then '<17' 
		when t1.age >= 18 and t1.age <= 23 then '18-23' 
		when t1.age >= 24 and t1.age <= 29 then '24-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 and t1.age <= 35 then '30-35' 
		when t1.age >= 36 and t1.age <= 40 then '36-40'
		when t1.age >= 41 and t1.age <= 45 then '41-45'
		when t1.age >= 46 and t1.age <= 50 then '46-50'
		else '>50' end as "Age Group"



from ret_stdnt_fact t1

select
DISTINCT 

case 
		when t1.act_score <= 20 then 'ACT 20 or less' 
		when t1.act_score >= 21 and t1.act_score <= 25 then 'ACT 21-25' 
		when t1.act_score >= 26 and t1.act_score <= 30 then 'ACT 26-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 then 'ACT 30 or more'
		else 'No ACT' end  as "ACT score"

from ret_stdnt_fact t1
order by 1
